120 	@Override
121 	public synchronized List<GovernmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary> readIncomeCsv() throws IOException {
122 		if (incomeCsvValues == null) {
123 			incomeCsvValues = readUsingZipInputStream(Request.Get(
124 				"https://www.esv.se/psidata/manadsutfall/GetFile/?documentType=Inkomst&fileType=Zip&fileName=M%C3%A5nadsutfall%20inkomster%20januari%202006%20-%20augusti%202018,%20definitivt.zip&year=2018&month=8&status=Definitiv")
125 				.execute().returnContent().asStream(),SPECIFIC_OUTGOING_FIELDS);
126 		}
127 		return Collections.unmodifiableList(incomeCsvValues);
128 	}
129 	
130 	@Override
131 	public synchronized List<GovernmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary> readOutgoingCsv() throws IOException {		
132 		if (outGoingCsvValues == null) {
133 			outGoingCsvValues = readUsingZipInputStream(Request.Get(
134 				"https://www.esv.se/psidata/manadsutfall/GetFile/?documentType=Utgift&fileType=Zip&fileName=M%C3%A5nadsutfall%20utgifter%20januari%202006%20-%20augusti%202018,%20definitivt.zip&year=2018&month=8&status=Definitiv")
135 				.execute().returnContent().asStream(),SPECIFIC_INCOMING_FIELDS);
136 		}
137 		return Collections.unmodifiableList(outGoingCsvValues);
138 	}
139 
140 	/**
141 	 * Read using zip input stream.
142 	 *
143 	 * @param inputStream
144 	 *            the input stream
145 	 * @param specificFields
146 	 *            the specific fields
147 	 * @return the list
148 	 * @throws IOException
149 	 *             Signals that an I/O exception has occurred.
150 	 */
151 	private List<GovernmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary> readUsingZipInputStream(final InputStream inputStream,final String[] specificFields) throws IOException {		
152 		final BufferedInputStream bis = new BufferedInputStream(inputStream);
153 		final ZipInputStream is = new ZipInputStream(bis);
154 
155 		final List<GovernmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary> list = new ArrayList<>();
156 		try {
157 			ZipEntry entry;
158 			while ((entry = is.getNextEntry()) != null) {
159 				list.addAll(readCsvContent(is,specificFields));
160 			}
161 		} finally {
162 			is.close();
163 		}
164 		return list;
165 	}
166 
167 	/**
168 	 * Read csv content.
169 	 *
170 	 * @param is
171 	 *            the is
172 	 * @param specificFields
173 	 *            the specific fields
174 	 * @return the list
175 	 * @throws IOException
176 	 *             Signals that an I/O exception has occurred.
177 	 */
178 	private List<GovernmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary> readCsvContent(final InputStream is,final String[] specificFields) throws IOException {
179 		final CSVParser parser = CSVParser.parse(new InputStreamReader(is,Charsets.UTF_8), CSVFormat.EXCEL.withHeader().withDelimiter(';'));
180 		final List<CSVRecord> records = parser.getRecords();
181 		records.remove(0);
182 		
183 		Map<Integer, Map<String,String>> orgMinistryMap = createOrgMinistryMap(esvExcelReader.getDataPerMinistry(null));
184 		
185 		final List<GovernmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary> list = new ArrayList<>();
186 		
187 		for (final CSVRecord csvRecord : records) {
188 			final GovernmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummaryhtml#GovernmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary">GovernmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary = new GovernmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary(csvRecord.get(MYNDIGHET), csvRecord.get(ORGANISATIONSNUMMER), orgMinistryMap.get(Integer.parseInt(csvRecord.get(YEAR))).get(csvRecord.get(ORGANISATIONSNUMMER).replaceAll("-", "")), Integer.parseInt(csvRecord.get(YEAR)));
189 			
190 			for (final String field : specificFields) {				
191 				governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary.addDescriptionField(field,csvRecord.get(field));
192 			}
193 			
194 			addResultForMonth(governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary,Month.JANUARY.getValue(),csvRecord.get(UTFALL_JANUARI));
195 			addResultForMonth(governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary,Month.FEBRUARY.getValue(),csvRecord.get(UTFALL_FEBRUARI));
196 			addResultForMonth(governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary,Month.MARCH.getValue(),csvRecord.get(UTFALL_MARS));
197 			
198 			addResultForMonth(governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary,Month.APRIL.getValue(),csvRecord.get(UTFALL_APRIL));
199 			addResultForMonth(governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary,Month.MAY.getValue(),csvRecord.get(UTFALL_MAJ));
200 			addResultForMonth(governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary,Month.JUNE.getValue(),csvRecord.get(UTFALL_JUNI));
201 			
202 			addResultForMonth(governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary,Month.JULY.getValue(),csvRecord.get(UTFALL_JULI));
203 			addResultForMonth(governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary,Month.AUGUST.getValue(),csvRecord.get(UTFALL_AUGUSTI));
204 			addResultForMonth(governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary,Month.SEPTEMBER.getValue(),csvRecord.get(UTFALL_SEPTEMBER));
205 			
206 			addResultForMonth(governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary,Month.OCTOBER.getValue(),csvRecord.get(UTFALL_OKTOBER));
207 			addResultForMonth(governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary,Month.NOVEMBER.getValue(),csvRecord.get(UTFALL_NOVEMBER));
208 			addResultForMonth(governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary,Month.DECEMBER.getValue(),csvRecord.get(UTFALL_DECEMBER));
209 			
210 			list.add(governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary);
211 		}
212 		
213 		return list;
214 	}
215 
216 	/**
217 	 * Creates the org ministry map.
218 	 *
219 	 * @param data the data
220 	 * @return the map
221 	 */
222 	private static Map<Integer, Map<String, String>> createOrgMinistryMap(
223 			Map<Integer, List<GovernmentBodyAnnualSummary>> data) {
224 		Map<Integer, Map<String,String>> orgMinistryMap = new HashMap<>();
225 		
226 		Set<Entry<Integer, List<GovernmentBodyAnnualSummary>>> entrySet = data.entrySet();
227 		
228 		for (Entry<Integer, List<GovernmentBodyAnnualSummary>> entry : entrySet) {		
229 			orgMinistryMap.put(entry.getKey(), entry.getValue().stream().collect(Collectors.groupingBy(t -> t.getOrgNumber().replaceAll("-","") ,Collectors.collectingAndThen(
230                     Collectors.toList(), 
231                     values -> values.get(0).getMinistry()))));
232 		}
233 		
234 		return orgMinistryMap;
235 	}
236 
237 	/**
238 	 * Adds the result for month.
239 	 *
240 	 * @param governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary
241 	 *            the government body annual outcome summary
242 	 * @param month
243 	 *            the month
244 	 * @param value
245 	 *            the value
246 	 */
247 	private static void addResultForMonth(final GovernmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary, final int month,
248 			final String value) {
249 		if (value != null && value.length() >0 ) {
250 			governmentBodyAnnualOutcomeSummary.addData(month,Double.valueOf(value.replaceAll(",", ".")));
251 		}
252 	}
